<section id="licensing">
  <h1>Licensing & Sponsorship</h1>
  <p>Bullseye2D's core is licensed under the <span class="hl">MIT License</span>, offering <span class="hl">freedom</span> to use, modify, and distribute your games.

  </p>
  <p>For advanced features and to <span class="hl">support the project</span>, we offer a <span class="hl">Premium Edition</span>. Purchasing a license gives access to extra features and fuels Bullseye2D's ongoing development. Premium features may transition to the MIT core over time.</p>
  <p>But all important things you need to build and publish games are for <span class="hl">free</span> in the MIT core; a license is <span class="hl">no requirement.</span></p>

