        <li>You're a <span class="hl">hobbyist</span> not earning income from your projects (please outline your project).</li>
        <li>You're <span class="hl">under 18</span>.</li>
        <li>You're a <span class="hl">student</span> (school, college, bootcamp, or online course)</li>
        <li>You're a <span class="hl">teacher, mentor, or parent</span> teaching kids to code.
        </li>
        <li>You work(ed) in <span class="hl">public service</span> or for a <span class="hl">non-profit organization</span>.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </details>

